<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200819/dfd898fdf715486186a11504fc163006.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>首先我们来看看价格：华为MateBook X起步价7999元，华为MateBook 13锐龙版起步价4599元，华为MateBook 14起步价4999元。</p>
